    g_c11d37: "Service improvement: Analysis of service usage statistics and improvement of service quality",
    g_881717: "Notice\\xB7Notice: Sending essential notifications such as class schedule changes, closure date information, etc.",
    g_09d2fa: "Article 2 (Personal information items processed)",
