    g_970bac: "Article 4 (Provision of personal information to third parties)",
    g_cf1c56: "The company processes the personal information of the information subject only within the scope specified in Article 1, and does not provide personal information to third parties except in cases such as the consent of the information subject or special provisions of the law.",
    g_3b33b8: "Article 5 (Entrustment of personal information processing work)",
